	      	<h2 class="text-center process">ASEPTIC PACKAGING</h2>
	      	<p class="text-center">This technology uses time, temperature, and hermetic sealing to create fully sterile beverages without need for preservatives. Each Elmhurst carton is shelf stable and can be safely stored at room temperature until opened.</p>
	      	</section>

