	      	<h2 class="text-center process">VERSATILITY</h2>
	      	<p class="text-center">Elmhurst products are versatile, with a variety of uses beyond drinking and cereal. These may include everything from coffee to cooking; smoothies to soups. Our cashew milk, for instance, works to barista standards in coffee, and can also be used in baking and sauces.</p>
