	      	<h2 class="text-center process">SUSTAINABILITY</h2>
	      	<p class="text-center">HydroRelease is a zero waste process, meaning all parts of the grain, nut, or seed are used. Our cartons are certified by the Forest Stewardship Council and 100% recyclable in most US homes. Plant-based foods generally have a lower carbon footprint than their animal counterparts.</p>
